ren mientras no haga la entrega en la forma indicada y el arrendador sede por recibido a su entera satisfacción de la misma.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;tab-stops:216.0pt"><span style="font-size:7.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:8.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;tab-stops:216.0pt"><span style="font-size:7.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:8.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;tab-stops:216.0pt"><span style="font-size:7.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:8.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">DÉCIMA. - FIADOR </span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;tab-stops:216.0pt"><span style="font-size:7.0pt;m