&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX"> <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto; text-align:justify;line-height:normal;tab-stops:216.0pt"><span style="font-size:7.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:8.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">“EL ARRENDATARIO” al desocuparse obliga a entregar la localidad materia de este contrato mediante aviso prescrito con acuse de recibo, en el domicilio del arrendador, subsistiendo su obligación de pagar la renta y sus accesorios que se generen mientras no hágala entrega en la forma indicada y el arrendador sede por recibido a su entera satisfacción de la misma.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX"> <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto; text-align:justify;line-height:normal;tab-stops:216.0pt"><span style="font-size:7.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:8.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX"> <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto; text-align:justify;line-height:normal;tab-stops:216.0pt"><span style="font-size:7.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:8.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:ES-MX">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-fami